claim.claim-text:
1. A method for forming a tantalum oxide capacitor comprising: 
forming a nitride layer by nitriding an upper surface of a lower electrode; 
depositing a tantalum-nitride layer on the nitride layer by an atomic layer deposition (ALD) method; 
forming a tantalum oxide layer by oxidizing the tantalum-nitride layer; and 
forming an upper electrode on the tantalum oxide layer.
